{"tid":681323,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"使用ThreadRipper（包括Ryzen） 請關閉HPET以解決各種lag問題","createTime":"2018-05-28T02:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:29:05.000Z","uid":58882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd598c78a91dc2375961e6b488fbec7fbbf1547e","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"ThreadRipper一定要關HPET。原因可能是HPET與driver或系統功能有衝突。開著HPET，很多遊戲都會莫名其妙的lag。運行這些lag的遊戲之後退出時，Windows任務管理器性能頁面看CPU 佔用率，會很奇怪的有百分之十幾的佔用率（正常應該是0％〜1％）。nvme ssd用作跑分，4k-64分數會出奇的低，延遲也很高。另外跑CINEBENCH的時候畫面也會偶爾卡住那麼一兩秒.windows進桌面之前轉圈也會卡兩次。<br />\n<br />\n關閉之後就一切順滑如絲了。關閉方法：命令提示符（管理員）內執行bcdedit / set useplatformclock false，即可關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n系統剛裝完默認沒開這個的。但是如果你運行了RyzenMaster，抱歉，就開了，無盡的卡頓等著你。"},{"pid":"64222d65ad79472604842d52180325a4d1b57a2f","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ThreadRipper一定要關HPET。原因可能是HPET與driver或系統功能有衝突。開著HPET，很多遊戲都會莫名其妙的lag。運行這些lag的遊戲之後退出時，Windows任務管理器性能頁面看CPU 佔用率，會很奇怪的有百分之十幾的佔用率（正常應該是0％〜1％）。nvme ssd用作跑分，4k-64分數會出奇的低，延遲也很高。另外跑CINEBENCH的時候畫面也會偶爾lag住那麼一兩秒.windows進桌面之前轉圈也會lag 兩次。<br />\n<br />\n關閉之後就一切順暢了。<br />\n關閉方法：命令提示符（管理員）內執行bcdedit / set useplatformclock false，即可關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n系統剛裝完默認沒開這個的。但是如果你運行了RyzenMaster，抱歉，就開了，無盡的<del>卡頓</del>lag等著你。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"143eb12dd52ae903baa8352e2fc0ce44a8c72e22","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/105818_4e3d92c2f653206a16914933f3d76cf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F105818_4e3d92c2f653206a16914933f3d76cf3.png&h=dc550932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/105819_232a6ff112941ca4af6574ed74189ead.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F105819_232a6ff112941ca4af6574ed74189ead.png&h=36822daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad915b22013412d7c093049f98abf5e799ecde3e","tid":681323,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"RyzenMaster本身就冇用(識超頻就去bios, 唔識就唔好搞咁多), 唔裝就冇事"},{"pid":"49f2247b1d1bc89a6825f3b1494a4fe87ae036cb","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad915b22013412d7c093049f98abf5e799ecde3e","tid":681323,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"RyzenMaster本身就冇用(識超頻就去bios, 唔識就唔好搞咁多), 唔裝就冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"唔裝ryzen master 都有hept預設開左"},{"pid":"7a5fb5deb25105f7e333f0da6ff0ee1be8fc5e12","tid":681323,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"要入埋bios disable"},{"pid":"b8a7676321bdb7274aab63236d98cdacb2de2c8b","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a5fb5deb25105f7e333f0da6ff0ee1be8fc5e12","tid":681323,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"要入埋bios disable"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"我用c7h  asus 冇show出來要用cmd解決"},{"pid":"e662b7a456d2d926d58b3774610d0ccd9c241d02","tid":681323,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"push"}]}